\begin_layout Subsection*

\lang english
1.
 Purpose
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard

\lang english
This policy governs the mandatory postmortem review process conducted following every cybersecurity incident declared under Chapter 4 authority.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Subsection*

\lang english
2.
 Scope
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard

\lang english
This policy applies to all Information Operations Department personnel who participated in or supported cybersecurity incident response operations,
 and to the IT Director and Assistant IT Director in their governance roles over the postmortem review process.
\end_layout

